review.reviewBody: Mashallah. Very delicious pizza. Highly recommended. Halal
Really goodfood  I enjoyed a lot
kheer rice was raw, beef rolls tasted weird and chicken Biryani was burnt taste first time disappointing order didn't enjoy any of these.
Thank you 777 for a fresh, hot and tasty meal. The Fritou Burger with mojos were perfect and on time. Jazak Allah.
The Chili Cheese fries were nice, it would be best if the cheese was less salty. great portion.
